OL,4,CFrance announces ban on outside heaters
OL,5, France's government has announced new
OL,6, environmental measures, including a ban
OL,7, on heated terraces for cafes and bars.
OL,9,FEcology Minister Barbara Pompili said
OL,10,Foutside heating or air conditioning was
OL,11,Fan "ecological aberration".
OL,13,FThe ban will not come into force until
OL,14,Fafter the winter as restaurants have
OL,15,Fbeen hard hit by Covid-19, she added.
OL,17,FAll heated or air-conditioned buildings
OL,18,Fopen to the public will also have to
OL,19,Fkeep their doors closed to avoid
OL,20,Fwasting energy.
